Noto Sans KR
------------
This application bundles a subset of the Noto Sans KR variable font
(shared/src/commonMain/composeResources/font/notosanskr.ttf), used to render
Korean (Hangul) and Latin text.

Copyright 2014-2021 Adobe (http://www.adobe.com/), with Reserved Font Name
"Source Han Sans" / Noto Sans CJK.

Licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1. The full license text is
bundled with the app at composeResources/files/notosanskr_OFL.txt and is
available at https://scripts.sil.org/OFL.

The bundled font is a subset (Latin-1 + Hangul Jamo/Syllables + common
punctuation) of the upstream variable font to reduce payload size; the wght axis
(100–900) is retained so Regular/Medium/Bold weights render from a single file.
